msgstr "<para>Eden</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To play patience you need, as the name suggests, patience. For simple games, "
"where the way the game goes depends only upon how the cards fall, your "
"patience might be the only thing you need."
msgstr ""
"Če želite igrati potrpežljivost, potrebujete, kot že ime pove, "
"potrpežljivost. Pri preprostih igrah, kjer je potek igre odvisen samo od "
"tega, kako padajo karte, je morda edina stvar, ki jo potrebujete, vaša "
"potrpežljivost."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are also patience games where you must plan your strategy and think "
"ahead in order to win."
msgstr ""
"Obstajajo tudi igre potrpežljivosti, kjer morate načrtovati svojo strategijo "
"in razmišljati vnaprej, da lahko zmagate."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A theme common to all the games is the player must put the cards in a "
"special order &mdash; moving, turning and reordering them."
msgstr ""
"Tema, ki je skupna vsem igram, je, da mora igralec karte postaviti v poseben "
"vrstni red &mdash; premikanje, obračanje in preurejanje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to Play"
msgstr "Kako igrati"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:116
#, no-c-format
msgid "Objective:"
msgstr "Cilj:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:116
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rearrange the cards by suit in as few moves as possible."
msgstr "Prerazporedite karte glede na barvo v čim manj potezah."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As &kpatience; offers you a multiplicity of different solitaire games, there "
"is no straightforward how-to which could fit all of them. Therefore, it is "
"essential that you read each individual subsection of Game Rules, Strategies "
"and Tips section before you start playing a version you are not familiar "
"with."
msgstr ""
"Kot &kpatience; vam ponuja množico različnih iger pasjanse, ni enostavnega "
"navodila, ki bi ustrezalo vsem. Zato je bistveno, da preberete vsak "
"posamezen pododdelek razdelka Pravila igre, strategije in nasveti, preden "
"začnete igrati različico, ki je ne poznate."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Essentially there are two types of solitaire games – the ones that let you "
"arrange the cards by same color and the ones that let you arrange the cards "
"by alternating color. You can easily determine which game you are trying out "
"using trial-and-error method. Once you know which one you are dealing with "
"the rest is easy; keep arranging and rearranging the cards and collecting "
"the matching ones."
msgstr ""
"V bistvu obstajata dve vrsti iger pasjanse – tiste, ki vam omogočajo, da "
"karte razporedite po isti barvi, in tiste, ki vam omogočajo, da karte "
"razporedite po izmenični barvi. Z metodo poskusov in napak lahko preprosto "
"ugotovite, katero igro preizkušate. Ko enkrat veste, s katero imate opravka, "
"je ostalo enostavno; nadaljujte z urejanjem in preurejanjem kart ter "
"zbiranjem ujemajočih se."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"From the beginning, however, pay attention to your card stacks. Do not rush "
"to move individual cards around. See if it might be more useful elsewhere."
msgstr ""
"Od začetka pa bodite pozorni na svoje kupe kart. Ne hitite s premikanjem "
"posameznih kart. Poglejte, če bi bilo morda bolj uporabno kje drugje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For additional help you can also take quick peeks onto the statusbar. Each "
"of the games has a built in solver which informs you whether the game you "
"are currently playing can be completed or not. If you see that solver could "
"not complete the current game, chances are you will not be able to do so as "
"well. At this point you can either restart the current game, or start a "
"completely new game."
msgstr ""
"Za dodatno pomoč lahko tudi hitro pokukate v vrstico stanja. Vsaka od iger "
"ima vgrajenega reševalca, ki vas obvesti, ali je igro, ki jo trenutno "
"igrate, mogoče dokončati ali ne. Če vidite, da reševalec ni mogel dokončati "
"trenutne igre, je verjetno, da tudi vi tega ne boste mogli storiti. Na tej "
"točki lahko znova zaženete trenutno igro ali začnete povsem novo igro."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid "Note:"
msgstr "Opomba:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Playing solitaire games helps you to greatly improve your attention span and "
"enhance the ability to concentrate."
msgstr ""
"Igranje pasjanse vam pomaga močno izboljšati razpon pozornosti in izboljšati "
"sposobnost koncentracije."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Rules, Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Pravila igre, strategije in nasveti"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid "General Rules"
msgstr "Splošna pravila"

#. Tag: primary
#: index.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid "suits"
msgstr "barve kart"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A card game contains one or more card decks of 52 cards each. Each deck "
"contains the four suits:"
msgstr ""
"Igra s kartami vsebuje enega ali več kompletov kart po 52 kart. Vsak komplet "
"vsebuje štiri barve:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid "Clubs"
msgstr "Križi"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spades"
msgstr "Piki"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hearts"
msgstr "Srca"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid "Diamonds"
msgstr "Kare"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each of these suits contains the following card types: ace, two, three, "
"four, five, six, seven, eight, nine, ten, jack, queen, and king."
msgstr ""
"Vsaka od teh barv vsebuje naslednje vrste kart: asa, dvojko, trojko, "
"štirico, petico, šestico, sedmico, osmico, devetko, desetico, fanta, damo in "
"kralja."

#. Tag: primary
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid "family"
msgstr "družina"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This complete order of cards is called a family. There are real families and "
"alternating ones. The real families are all of one suit (&eg; Hearts). In "
"the alternating families the card color changes from one to another, between "
"a black color (Clubs and Spades) and a red color (Hearts and Diamonds)."
msgstr ""
"Ta popolni vrstni red kart se imenuje družina. Obstajajo prave družine in "
"izmenične. Prave družine so vse iste barve (npr. Srca). V izmeničnih "
"družinah se barva kart spreminja od ene do druge, med črno barvo (Križi in "
"Piki) ter rdečo barvo (Srca in Kare)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid "If the family is not complete it is called a sequence."
msgstr "Če družina ni popolna, se imenuje zaporedje."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid "The game field of &kpatience;"
msgstr "Igralno polje &kpatience;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are a number of features found in typical patience games. These are "
"described below."
msgstr ""
"Tipične igre potrpežljivosti vsebujejo številne funkcije. Ti so opisani "
"spodaj."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid "1. Talon"
msgstr "1. Talon"

#. Tag: primary
#: index.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid "talon"
msgstr "talon"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the beginning of each game all cards are mixed in the deck. In some games "
"not all cards are dealt out. The remaining cards are put down on the talon "
"(also called the stock). You can find this quite easily, since in most games "
"it is the only pile in which all cards are face down."
msgstr ""
"Na začetku vsake igre se vse karte zmešajo v plošči. V nekaterih igrah niso "
"razdeljene vse karte. Preostale karte se odložijo na talon (imenovan tudi "
"zaloga). To lahko najdete precej enostavno, saj je v večini iger to edini "
"kup, v katerem so vse karte obrnjene navzdol."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:172
#, no-c-format
msgid "2. Waste Pile"
msgstr "2. Kup odpadkov"

#. Tag: primary
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "waste pile"
msgstr "kup odpadkov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Many games use a waste pile to hold cards taken from the talon. Typically "
"clicking on the talon will cause the topmost card to be flipped face up and "
"placed on the waste pile, at which point the card enters play."
msgstr ""
"Veliko iger uporablja kup odpadkov za shranjevanje kart, vzetih iz talona. "
"Običajno klik na talon povzroči, da se najvišja karta obrne z licem navzgor "
"in odloži na kup odpadkov, na kateri točki vstopi karta v igro."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "3. Foundation"
msgstr "3. Temelj"

#. Tag: primary
#: index.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid "foundation"
msgstr "temelj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The foundation piles are where you want your cards to end up. Typically, the "
"game is won only once all cards have been moved to the foundation piles in "
"the correct order. The number of foundation piles and the ordering required "
"varies from game to game."
msgstr ""
"Temeljni skupki kart so tam, kjer želite, da končajo vaše karte. Običajno je "
"igra zmagana šele, ko so vse karte premaknjene na temeljne kupe v pravilnem "
"vrstnem redu. Število temeljnih skupkov in potreben vrstni red se "
"razlikujeta od igre do igre."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Most games start with the foundation piles empty. Choosing the "
"<guimenuitem>Drop</guimenuitem> action from the menu or toolbar will cause "
"&kpatience; to scan through all the piles move as many cards to the "
"foundation piles as it can. If you have the <guimenuitem>Enabled Autodrop</"
"guimenuitem> setting activated, &kpatience; will attempt to perform a drop "
"whenever possible."
msgstr ""
"Večina iger se začne s praznimi temeljnimi skupki. Če v meniju ali orodni "
"vrstici izberete dejanje <guimenuitem>Spusti</guimenuitem>, bo &kpatience; "
"za pregledovanje vseh kupov premakni čim več kart na temeljne kupe. Če imate "
"aktivirano nastavitev <guimenuitem>Omogočeno samodejno polaganje</"
"guimenuitem>, &kpatience; bo poskušal izvesti polaganje, kadar koli bo to "
"mogoče."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid "4. Playing Piles"
msgstr "4. Igranje kupčkov"

#. Tag: primary
#: index.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid "playing piles"
msgstr "igranje kupčkov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These piles are those where the actual reordering happens. The rules for "
"these piles vary a lot between games. Some show all cards on them, some do "
"not. Some allow only one card to be removed, some allow every card to be "
"removed, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Ti kupčki so tisti, kjer pride do dejanskega preurejanja. Pravila za te "
"kupčke se med igrami zelo razlikujejo. Nekateri prikazujejo vse karte, drugi "
"ne. Nekateri dovoljujejo odstranitev samo ene karte, nekateri pa odstranitev "
"vseh kart &etc;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rules for Individual Games"
msgstr "Pravila za posamezne igre"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Klondike</title>"
msgstr "<title>Klondike</title>"

#. Tag: primary
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid "<primary>Klondike</primary>"
msgstr "<primary>Klondike</primary>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Klondike is the most famous patience &mdash; most likely because it comes "
"with a well-known operating system. It is played with one deck."
msgstr ""
"Klondike je najbolj znana potrpežljivost &mdash; najverjetneje zato, ker "
"prihaja z znanim operacijskim sistemom. Igra se z enim kompletom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The goal in Klondike is to put all cards, as real families, ascending on the "
"foundation. This gets easier once all cards are lying face up in the playing "
"piles."
msgstr ""
"Cilj v Klondiku je postaviti vse karte kot prave družine navzgor na temelje. "
"To postane lažje, ko so vse karte v igralnih kupčkih obrnjene navzgor."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The sequences on the playing piles have to be put there in descending order. "
"The cards should alternate in colors (red and black). You can move whole "
"sequences or parts of it, if the first card fits on another pile."
msgstr ""
"Zaporedja na igralnih kupčkih morajo biti postavljena v padajočem vrstnem "
"redu. Barve kart naj se izmenjujejo (rdeča in črna). Lahko premaknete "
"celotno zaporedje ali njegove dele, če se prva karta prilega drugemu kupu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On a free pile you can put a king of any color, or a sequence starting with "
"a king."
msgstr ""
"Na prosti kupček lahko postavite kralja katere koli barve ali zaporedje, ki "
"se začne s kraljem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you click on the talon, one card from it will be moved to the waste "
"pile. You can move it to the playing piles or the foundation from there. If "
"the talon is empty, you can move the complete waste pile to the talon by "
"clicking on the empty talon."
msgstr ""
"Ko kliknete talon, se ena karta iz njega premakne na kup odpadkov. Od tam ga "
"lahko premaknete na igralne kupe ali temelj. Če je talon prazen, lahko "
"premaknete celoten kup smeti v talon s klikom na prazen talon."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can look through the cards on the talon as much as you like."
msgstr "Karte na talonu lahko pregledujete, kolikor želite."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Grandfather</title>"
msgstr "<title>Dedek</title>"

#. Tag: primary
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid "<primary>Grandfather</primary>"
msgstr "<primary>Dedek</primary>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This game was introduced to &Paul-Olav.Tvete;, the original developer of "
"&kpatience;, by his grandfather; it is named after this. No other patience "
"games are known to implement this patience game variant."
msgstr ""
"To igro je &Paul-Olav.Tvete;, izvirnemu razvijalcu &kpatience;, predstavil "
"njegov dedek; po tem se imenuje. Nobena druga potrpežljiva igra ni znana, da "
"bi izvajala to različico potrpežljive igre."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In Grandfather, one deck is dealt to seven playing piles. Some cards on each "
"pile are face down on the initial deal."
msgstr ""
"V igri Dedek se en komplet razdeli sedmim igralnim kupčkom. Nekatere karte "
"na vsakem kupu so pri začetni delitvi obrnjene navzdol."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The goal is to put all cards as real families ascending on the foundation "
"piles."
msgstr ""
"Cilj je postaviti vse karte kot prave družine, ki se dvigajo na temeljne "
"skupke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can move every card on every pile if it fits on another card, to build a "
"real sequence of descending order. For example, you can move the five of "
"spades on top of the six of spades, no matter how many cards on are on top "
"of the five of spades. Just the six of spades has to be on top of its pile."
msgstr ""
"Vsako karto lahko premaknete na vsakem kupu, če se prilega drugi karti, da "
"sestavite pravo zaporedje v padajočem vrstnem redu. Na primer, pikovo petico "
"lahko premaknete na pikovo šestico, ne glede na to, koliko kart je na vrhu "
"pikove petice. Samo pikova šestica mora biti na vrhu svojega kupa."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On a free pile you can place a king (again no matter how many cards are on "
"top of it)."
msgstr ""
"Na prosti kupček lahko postavite kralja (spet ne glede na to, koliko kart je "
"na vrhu)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If there are no more possible moves, you can redeal the cards. A redeal "
"consists of picking up the cards from the playing piles (pile by pile, left "
"to right) and redealing them in the starting pattern (zigzagging rows of "
"face down cards forming a peak and then left to right rows of face up cards "
"on top). Note that the cards are <emphasis>not</emphasis> shuffled and that "
"cards on the foundation piles are left untouched. You may redeal no more "
"than twice in a single game."
msgstr ""
"Če ni več možnih potez, lahko ponovno delite karte. Ponovna delitev je "
"sestavljena iz pobiranja kart iz igralnih kupčkov (kupček za kupčkom, od "
"leve proti desni) in njihovega ponovnega razdeljevanja po začetnem vzorcu "
"(cikcakaste vrste obrnjenih kart navzdol, ki tvorijo vrh, nato pa od leve "
"proti desni vrstice obrnjenih kart na vrhu ). Upoštevajte, da karte "
"<emphasis>niso</emphasis> premešane in da karte na temeljnih skupkih "
"ostanejo nedotaknjene. V eni igri lahko znova delite največ dvakrat."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Even though the rules are simple and allow many moves, the game is still "
"hard to win. Despite this, or because of it, this game remains a joy to play."
msgstr ""
"Čeprav so pravila preprosta in dovoljujejo veliko potez, je igro vseeno "
"težko zmagati. Kljub temu ali prav zaradi tega je ta igra še vedno užitek "
"igrati."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Aces Up</title>"
msgstr "<title>Aces Up</title>"

#. Tag: primary
#: index.docbook:274
#, no-c-format
msgid "<primary>Aces Up</primary>"
msgstr "<primary>Aces Up</primary>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:274
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This patience has simple rules, yet is hard to win. It is played with one "
"deck. The goal is to put all cards besides aces onto the foundation. There "
"should be an ace left on every playing pile afterwards."
msgstr ""
"Ta potrpežljivost ima preprosta pravila, vendar jo je težko osvojiti. Igra "
"se z enim kompletom. Cilj je postaviti vse karte razen asov na temelj. Nato "
"mora na vsakem igralnem kupčku ostati as."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each top card that is of the same suit (&eg; spades) and has a lower value "
"than another top card (&eg; six of spades and four of spades) can be put on "
"the foundation by clicking on it."
msgstr ""
"Vsako zgornjo karto, ki je iste barve (npr. pik) in ima nižjo vrednost kot "
"druga zgornja karta (npr. pik šest in štiri), lahko postavite na temelj s "
"klikom nanjo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you cannot move any more cards to the foundation, you can get a new card "
"for each playing pile by clicking on the talon."
msgstr ""
"Če ne morete premakniti več kart na temelj, lahko dobite novo karto za vsak "
"igralni kup s klikom na talon."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:291
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On a free pile you can move every other card on top of a pile. You should "
"use these moves to free piles. That way, new cards can be moved to the "
"foundation."
msgstr ""
"Na prostem kupu lahko premaknete vsako drugo karto na vrh kupa. Te poteze bi "
"morali uporabiti za osvobajanje kupčkov. Na ta način je mogoče nove kartice "
"premakniti v temelj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:296 index.docbook:384
#, no-c-format
msgid "The auto drop feature is disabled in this patience game."
msgstr ""
"Funkcija samodejnega spuščanja je v tej igri potrpežljivosti onemogočena."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:303
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Freecell</title>"
msgstr "<title>Freecell</title>"

#. Tag: primary
#: index.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid "<primary>Freecell</primary>"
msgstr "<primary>Freecell</primary>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Freecell is played with one card deck. You have four free cells in the top "
"left corner. In addition there are four foundation piles, and eight playing "
"piles below."
msgstr ""
"Freecell se igra z enim kompletom kart. V zgornjem levem kotu imate štiri "
"proste celice. Poleg tega so še štirje temeljni piloti in osem igralnih "
"skupkov spodaj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The goal of the game is to have all cards as real families ascending on the "
"foundation. You can achieve this often if you know how to play: Freecell is "
"solvable at a rate of 99.9% approximately &mdash; of the first 32,000 deals "
"there is only one unsolvable (11,982 if you want to know)."
msgstr ""
"Cilj igre je imeti vse karte kot prave družine, ki se dvignejo na temelj. To "
"lahko pogosto dosežete, če znate igrati: Freecell je rešljiv s stopnjo "
"približno 99,9 % &mdash; od prvih 32.000 deljenj je samo ena nerešljiva "
"(11.982, če ravno želite vedeti)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the playing piles you have to build descending sequences, where red and "
"black cards alternate. You can put any card in a free cell."
msgstr ""
"V igralnih kupčkih morate graditi padajoče nize, kjer se izmenjujejo rdeče "
"in črne karte. V prosto celico lahko postavite katero koli kartico."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can only move one card that lays on top of a pile or a free cell. "
"Sequences can only be moved if you have enough free space (either free cells "
"or free playing piles) to place the cards."
msgstr ""
"Premaknete lahko samo eno karto, ki je na vrhu kupa ali proste celice. "
"Zaporedja lahko premikate samo, če imate dovolj prostega prostora (bodisi "
"proste celice ali proste igralne kupčke) za postavitev kart."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid "The maximum amount of cards you can move is calculated by:"
msgstr "Največje število kart, ki jih lahko premaknete, se izračuna po:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:332
#, no-c-format
msgid "(#{free cells} + 1) * 2<superscript>#{free piles}</superscript>"
msgstr "(#{proste celice} + 1) * 2<superscript>#{prosti kupčki}</superscript>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:336 index.docbook:599 index.docbook:631
#, no-c-format
msgid "Variations:"
msgstr "Različice:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:338
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<quote>Baker's Game</quote> is like <quote>Freecell</quote>, but the piles "
"are built down by suit."
msgstr ""
"<quote>Baker's Game</quote> je kot <quote>Freecell</quote>, vendar so kupi "
"sestavljeni z barvo kart."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:339
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<quote>Eight Off</quote> is like <quote>Freecell</quote>, but the piles are "
"built down by suit. You have 8 reserves and only kings can fill empty "
"spaces. Four reserves are filled at game start."
msgstr ""
"<quote>Eight Off</quote> je kot <quote>Freecell</quote>, vendar so kupčki "
"zgrajeni z barvo kart. Imate 8 rezerv in samo kralji lahko zapolnijo prazna "
"mesta. Štiri rezerve so zapolnjene na začetku igre."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<quote>Forecell</quote> is like <quote>Freecell</quote>, but the reserves "
"are filled at game start, and only kings can fill empty spaces."
msgstr ""
"<quote>Forecell</quote> je kot <quote>Freecell</quote>, vendar se rezerve "
"zapolnijo na začetku igre in le kralji lahko zapolnijo prazna mesta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<quote>Seahaven Towers</quote> is like <quote>Freecell</quote>, but with 10 "
"piles which are built down by suit, and only kings can fill empty spaces. "
"Two reserves are filled at game start."
msgstr ""
"<quote>Seahaven Towers</quote> je kot <quote>Freecell</quote>, vendar z 10 "
"skupkov, ki so zgrajeni po barvi, prazna mesta pa lahko zapolnijo le kralji. "
"Dve rezervi se zapolnita na začetku igre."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:344
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To solve this game it is recommended to grab the cards out of the playing "
"sequences in the same order they have to be put into the foundation (first "
"the aces, then the twos, &etc;)"
msgstr ""
"Če želite rešiti to igro, je priporočljivo, da zgrabite karte iz igralnih "
"zaporedij v istem vrstnem redu, kot jih je treba postaviti v temelj (najprej "
"asi, nato dvojke itd.)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You should try to keep as many free cells and/or playing piles empty, so you "
"can build sequences as long as possible."
msgstr ""
"Potrudite se, da bo čim več prostih celic in/ali igralnih kupčkov praznih, "
"da boste lahko gradili zaporedja čim dlje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Mod3</title>"
msgstr "<title>Mod3</title>"

#. Tag: primary
#: index.docbook:360
#, no-c-format
msgid "<primary>Mod3</primary>"
msgstr "<primary>Mod3</primary>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:360
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Mod3 is played with two card decks. The goal is to put all cards on the top "
"three rows. In those you have to build sequences of the same color. In the "
"first row you have to create the sequence 2-5-8-J, in the second row the "
"sequence 3-6-9-Q, and in the third row the sequence 4-7-10-K. The suit of "
"the cards must be the same in each sequence, so you can only put a five of "
"hearts on top of a two of hearts."
msgstr ""
"Mod3 se igra z dvema kompletoma kart. Cilj je postaviti vse karte v zgornje "
"tri vrstice. V njih morate zgraditi zaporedja iste barve. V prvi vrsti "
"morate ustvariti zaporedje 2-5-8-J, v drugi vrsti zaporedje 3-6-9-Q in v "
"tretji vrsti zaporedje 4-7-10-K. Barva kart mora biti enaka v vsakem "
"zaporedju, tako da lahko na srčno dvojko položite samo petico."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:369
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The fourth row is both your waste pile and playing pile. On an empty slot "
"you can put any card from the first three rows, or one from the top of the "
"fourth row."
msgstr ""
"Četrta vrsta je vaš kup odpadkov in kup za igro. Na prazno režo lahko "
"vstavite katero koli karto iz prvih treh vrstic ali eno z vrha četrte "
"vrstice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:374
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can put aces on the aces piles, on top of the talon. They are in the "
"game so you have a starting point for creating free slots."
msgstr ""
"Ase lahko postavite na kupe asov, na vrh talona. So v igri, tako da imate "
"izhodišče za ustvarjanje brezplačnih igralnih avtomatov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:379
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you cannot move any more cards, you can get new cards on the fourth row "
"by clicking on the talon."
msgstr ""
"Če ne morete premakniti več kart, lahko dobite nove karte v četrti vrstici s "
"klikom na talon."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:390
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Normandy</title>"
msgstr "<title>Normandija</title>"

#. Tag: primary
#: index.docbook:392
#, no-c-format
msgid "<primary>Normandy</primary>"
msgstr "<primary>Normandija</primary>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:392
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Normandy is played with two card decks. The aim is to put all cards in real "
"families ascending on the foundation."
msgstr ""
"Normandija se igra z dvema kompletoma kart. Cilj je, da se vse karte "
"razporedijo v prave družine v naraščajočem vrstnem redu na podlagi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:397
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The playing piles have to be descending, while red and black cards have to "
"alternate. You can only move sequences or single cards. On a free slot you "
"can put any card or sequence."
msgstr ""
"Igralni kupčki se morajo padati, rdeče in črne karte pa se morajo "
"izmenjevati. Premikate lahko samo zaporedja ali posamezne karte. Na prosto "
"režo lahko postavite poljubno karto ali zaporedje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:403
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you cannot move any more cards, you can click on the talon to get new "
"cards on each playing pile."
msgstr ""
"Če ne morete premakniti več kart, lahko kliknete talon, da dobite nove karte "
"na vsakem igralnem kupu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:407
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In using the <guibutton>Undo</guibutton> feature you can ease the game quite "
"a lot, as you have to take many decisions and some of them might turn out to "
"be wrong after you clicked the talon."
msgstr ""
"Z uporabo funkcije <guibutton>Razveljavi</guibutton> lahko precej olajšate "
"igro, saj morate sprejeti veliko odločitev in nekatere od njih se lahko "
"izkažejo za napačne, potem ko kliknete talon."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:413
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This game is also known under the name \"Gypsy\", but because this term is "
"considered derogatory and offensive by many, we have chosen to use the "
"alternative name \"Normandy\" instead."
msgstr ""
"Ta igra je znana tudi pod imenom \"Cigan\", vendar ker mnogi menijo, da je "
"ta izraz slabšalni in žaljiv, smo se odločili za alternativno ime "
"\"Normandija\"."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:421
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Forty &amp; Eight</title>"
msgstr "<title>Štirideset &amp; Osem</title>"

#. Tag: primary
#: index.docbook:423
#, no-c-format
msgid "<primary>Forty &amp; Eight</primary>"
msgstr "<primary>Štirideset &amp; Osem</primary>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:423
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Forty &amp; Eight is played with two card decks. The goal is to put all "
"cards as real families on the foundation."
msgstr ""
"Štirideset &amp; Osmica se igra z dvema kompletoma kart. Cilj je postaviti "
"vse karte kot prave družine na temelj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:428
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The playing piles have to be descending. Colors are important. You can only "
"put a five of hearts on a six of hearts, for example."
msgstr ""
"Igralni kupčki se morajo spuščati. Barve so pomembne. Na srčno šestico lahko "
"na primer postavite samo petico."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:433
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can only move one card on top of a pile. You can put any card in a free "
"slot."
msgstr ""
"Na vrh kupa lahko premaknete samo eno karto. V prosto režo lahko vstavite "
"katero koli kartico."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:437
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By clicking on the talon you can put a card on the waste pile; from there "
"you can put it on a playing pile or the foundation (&kpatience; will do this "
"for you). If the talon is empty you can put all cards on the waste pile back "
"on the talon. This works only once: after the second time the talon empties, "
"the game is over."
msgstr ""
"S klikom na talon lahko odložite karto na kup odpadkov; od tam ga lahko "
"postavite na igralni kup ali temelj (&kpatience; bo to naredil namesto vas). "
"Če je talon prazen, lahko vrnete vse karte s kupa odpadkov nazaj na talon. "
"To deluje samo enkrat: ko se talon drugič izprazni, je igre konec."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:444
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This patience is difficult to solve. With some experience you can solve many "
"of the deals, especially if you use the <guibutton>Undo</guibutton> feature "
"from time to time to correct your decisions, and the decisions &kpatience; "
"makes in putting cards on the foundation."
msgstr ""
"To potrpežljivost je težko rešiti. Z nekaj izkušnjami lahko rešite veliko "
"poslov, zlasti če občasno uporabite funkcijo <guibutton>Razveljavi</"
"guibutton>, da popravite svoje odločitve, in odločitve &kpatience; naredi "
"pri polaganju kart na temelj."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:453
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Simple Simon</title>"
msgstr "<title>Preprosti Simon</title>"

#. Tag: primary
#: index.docbook:455
#, no-c-format
msgid "<primary>Simple Simon</primary>"
msgstr "<primary>Preprosti Simon</primary>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:455
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Simple Simon is played with one card deck. The goal is to put all cards as "
"real families on the foundation."
msgstr ""
"Preprosti Simon se igra z enim kompletom kart. Cilj je postaviti vse karte "
"kot prave družine na temelj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:460
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the playing piles you can build sequences. In general you don't have to "
"care about the suits of the cards, but sequences can only be moved if they "
"are part of a real sequence. For example, you can move the six of spades if "
"the five of <emphasis>spades</emphasis> is on top of it, but may not move it "
"if the five of <emphasis>clubs</emphasis> is on top of it."
msgstr ""
"V igralnih kupčkih lahko gradite zaporedja. Na splošno vam ni treba skrbeti "
"za barve kart, vendar lahko zaporedja premikate le, če so del pravega "
"zaporedja. Na primer, pikovo šestico lahko premaknete, če je petica "
"<emphasis>pik</emphasis> na vrhu, ne smete pa je premakniti, če je na vrhu "
"petica <emphasis>križa</emphasis> ."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:468
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The cards can only be moved to the foundation if all 13 cards of one family "
"lay on top of each other in the playing piles."
msgstr ""
"Karte je mogoče premakniti na temelj le, če vseh 13 kart ene družine leži "
"druga na drugi v igralnih kupčkih."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:474
#, no-c-format
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "Predlog"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:475
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You should try as soon as possible to move the cards to the correct piles, "
"to create free piles to place cards on temporarily, since you can put any "
"card on those."
msgstr ""
"Poskusite čim prej premakniti karte na pravilne kupčke, ustvariti proste "
"kupčke, na katere lahko začasno položite karte, saj lahko nanje postavite "
"katero koli karto."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:480
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With enough free room you can build families on free slots independently of "
"the color. If you have all cards in such families you can sort them by "
"color, so they can be moved to the foundation."
msgstr ""
"Z dovolj prostim prostorom lahko zgradite družine na prostih mestih "
"neodvisno od barve. Če imate vse karte v takšnih družinah, jih lahko "
"razvrstite po barvi, tako da jih lahko premaknete na temelj."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:489
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Yukon</title>"
msgstr "<title>Yukon</title>"

#. Tag: primary
#: index.docbook:491
#, no-c-format
msgid "<primary>Yukon</primary>"
msgstr "<primary>Yukon</primary>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:491
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yukon is played with one card deck. The goal is to put all cards as real "
"families ascending on the foundation."
msgstr ""
"Yukon se igra z enim kompletom kart. Cilj je postaviti vse karte kot prave "
"družine, ki se vzpenjajo na temelje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:496
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The sequences on the playing piles have to be descending with alternating "
"red and black cards. You can move every face up card no matter how many "
"cards are on top of it. So you can put a five of hearts on a six of spades "
"if that one is on top of its pile."
msgstr ""
"Zaporedja na igralnih kupčkih morajo biti padajoča z izmenjujočimi se "
"rdečimi in črnimi kartami. Premaknete lahko vsako obrnjeno karto navzgor, ne "
"glede na to, koliko kart je na njej. Torej lahko petico s pikami postavite "
"na pikovo šestico, če je ta na vrhu svojega kupa."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:502
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In a free slot you can put a king of any color (again, no matter how many "
"cards are on top of it)."
msgstr ""
"V prosto režo lahko postavite kralja katere koli barve (spet ne glede na to, "
"koliko kart je na vrhu)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:509
#, no-c-format
msgid "Grandfather's Clock"
msgstr "Dedkova ura"

#. Tag: primary
#: index.docbook:511
#, no-c-format
msgid "Grandfathers Clock"
msgstr "Dedkova ura"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:511
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Grandfather's clock is a simple patience game. With some experience you "
"should be able to solve most deals. It is played with one card deck. The aim "
"is to put the cards as real ascending sequences on the foundation."
msgstr ""
"Dedkova ura je preprosta igra potrpežljivosti. Z nekaj izkušnjami bi morali "
"rešiti večino poslov. Igra se z enim kompletom kart. Cilj je postaviti karte "
"kot prava naraščajoča zaporedja na temelj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:517
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The foundation is on the right-hand side and consists of 12 piles that form "
"the shape of a clock. The nine is at 12 o'clock, the queen is at 3 o'clock, "
"the three is at 6 o'clock and the six is at 9 o'clock."
msgstr ""
"Temelj je na desni strani in je sestavljen iz 12 skupkov, ki tvorijo obliko "
"ure. Devetka je ob 12. uri, dama ob 15. uri, trojka ob 18. uri in šestica ob "
"21. uri."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:523
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are 8 playing piles beside the clock and on each are 5 cards. On the "
"playing piles you can build descending sequences. The color of the cards is "
"not important. You can only move one card at a time."
msgstr ""
"Ob uri je 8 igralnih kupčkov in na vsakem je 5 kart. Na igralnih kupčkih "
"lahko gradite padajoče nize. Barva kart ni pomembna. Premaknete lahko le eno "
"karto naenkrat."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:532
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Golf</title>"
msgstr "<title>Golf</title>"

#. Tag: primary
#: index.docbook:534
#, no-c-format
msgid "<primary>Golf</primary>"
msgstr "<primary>Golf</primary>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:534
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Golf is played with one card deck. The goal of Golf is to move all the cards "
"on the tableau to the foundation."
msgstr ""
"Golf se igra z enim kompletom kart. Cilj igre Golf je premakniti vse karte "
"na mizi na temelj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:537
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The layout of golf solitaire is straightforward. At the beginning of the "
"game you will see the tableau. On it are seven columns each containing five "
"cards. The talon and the foundation are below."
msgstr ""
"Postavitev golf pasijanse je preprosta. Na začetku igre boste videli tabelo. "
"Na njem je sedem stolpcev, od katerih vsak vsebuje pet kart. Talon in temelj "
"sta spodaj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:541
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Playing golf solitaire is simple, but requires strategy to win. The cards at "
"the base of each column on the tableau are available for play. Available "
"cards are built upon the top foundation card in ascending or descending "
"sequence regardless of suit. If there are no moves available a card may be "
"dealt from the talon to the foundation. The game is over when all the cards "
"in the talon have been dealt and there are no more possible moves."
msgstr ""
"Igranje golf pasjanse je preprosto, vendar zahteva strategijo za zmago. "
"Karte na dnu vsakega stolpca na tabeli so na voljo za igro. Razpoložljive "
"karte so zgrajene na zgornji osnovni karti v naraščajočem ali padajočem "
"zaporedju, ne glede na barvo. Če ni na voljo nobenih potez, se lahko karta "
"razdeli od talona do temelja. Igre je konec, ko so vse karte v talonu "
"razdeljene in ni več možnih potez."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:550
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Spider</title>"
msgstr "<title>Pajek</title>"

#. Tag: primary
#: index.docbook:552
#, no-c-format
msgid "<primary>Spider</primary>"
msgstr "<primary>Pajek</primary>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:552
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Spider is played with two card decks. The cards are dealt out into 10 "
"playing piles, 4 of 6 cards and 6 of 5 cards each. This leaves 50 cards that "
"can be dealt out 10 at a time, one on each playing pile."
msgstr ""
"Pajek se igra z dvema kompletoma kart. Karte so razdeljene v 10 igralnih "
"kupčkov, po 4 od 6 kart in 6 od 5 kart. Tako ostane 50 kart, ki jih je "
"mogoče razdeliti po 10 hkrati, po eno na vsakem igralnem kupu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:558
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the playing piles, a card can be placed on another card of any suit and "
"of one higher value. A sequence of descending cards of the same suit may be "
"moved from one playing pile to another."
msgstr ""
"V igralnih kupčkih lahko karto položite na drugo karto poljubne barve in z "
"eno višjo vrednostjo. Zaporedje padajočih kart iste barve se lahko premika "
"iz enega igralnega kupa v drugega."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:564
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The goal of spider is to put all cards as real families descending from "
"Kings anywhere in the playing piles. When such a family is built in a "
"playing pile, it is removed to the lower-left corner of the window."
msgstr ""
"Cilj pajka je postaviti vse karte kot prave družine, ki izvirajo iz kraljev, "
"kamor koli v igralne kupe. Ko je taka družina sestavljena v igralni kup, se "
"le-ta odstrani v levi spodnji kot okna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:570
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The different levels determine how many suits are dealt - Easy uses 1 suit, "
"Medium uses 2 suits, and Hard uses all 4 suits. The game is fairly easy to "
"win at Easy level, and very difficult to win at Hard level."
msgstr ""
"Različne ravni določajo, koliko barv je razdeljenih - Enostavna uporabi 1 "
"barvo, srednja uporabi 2 barvi, težka pa uporabi vse 4 barve. Igro je dokaj "
"enostavno zmagati na preprosti ravni in zelo težko zmagati na težki ravni."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:579
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Baker's Dozen</title>"
msgstr "<title>Pekov ducat</title>"

#. Tag: primary
#: index.docbook:581
#, no-c-format
msgid "<primary>Baker's Dozen</primary>"
msgstr "<primary>Pekov ducat</primary>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:581
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Baker's Dozen is played with one card deck. The game's name originates from "
"the 13 columns in the game, the number in a baker's dozen. The cards are "
"dealt into columns of four on the tableau, resulting in 13 columns. Any king "
"that is in the top or middle of each column must be placed on the bottom "
"before the game starts. Two kings that are mixed into one column are placed "
"on the bottom without changing their order."
msgstr ""
"Pekov ducat se igra z enim kompletom kart. Ime igre izhaja iz 13 stolpcev v "
"igri, števila v pekovskem ducatu. Karte so razdeljene v stolpce po štiri na "
"tabeli, kar ima za posledico 13 stolpcev. Vsak kralj, ki je na vrhu ali "
"sredini vsakega stolpca, mora biti pred začetkom igre postavljen na dno. Dva "
"kralja, ki sta pomešana v en stolpec, sta postavljena na dno, ne da bi "
"spremenila njun vrstni red."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:590
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The object of the game is to build all the cards onto the four foundations "
"by suit, each from ace to king"
msgstr ""
"Cilj igre je sestaviti vse karte na štiri temelje po barvi, vsako od asa do "
"kralja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:594 index.docbook:626
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the playing piles you have to build descending sequences, regardless of "
"suit. You can only move one card that lays on top of a pile."
msgstr ""
"V igralnih kupih morate zgraditi padajoče zaporedje, ne glede na barvo. "
"Premaknete lahko le eno karto, ki je na vrhu kupa."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:601
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In <quote>Spanish Patience</quote>, any card can fill empty tableau spaces. "
"(In some sources, the foundations are built up regardless of suit)."
msgstr ""
"V <quote>Spanish Patience</quote> lahko katera koli karta zapolni prazne "
"prostore tabele. (V nekaterih virih se temelji gradijo ne glede na barvo)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:602
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<quote>Castles in Spain</quote> is akin to <quote>Spanish Patience</quote>, "
"but the cards in the tableau are built down by alternate color. In some "
"variations, the tableau is dealt face-down aside from the top cards of each "
"column."
msgstr ""
"<quote>Gradovi v Španiji</quote> je podoben <quote>Španski potrpežljivosti</"
"quote>, vendar so karte v tabeli sestavljene z nadomestno barvo. V nekaterih "
"različicah se tabela deli obrnjena navzdol poleg zgornjih kart vsakega "
"stolpca."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:603
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<quote>Portuguese Solitaire</quote> is halfway between <quote>Baker's Dozen</"
"quote> and <quote>Spanish Patience</quote> because empty columns can only be "
"filled with Kings."
msgstr ""
"<quote>Portugalska pasjansa</quote> je na pol poti med <quote>Pekovih ducat</"
"quote> in <quote>Špansko potrpežljivostjo</quote>, ker se prazne stolpce "
"lahko zapolni samo s kralji."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:606
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To solve this game it is recommended to grab the cards out of the playing "
"sequences in the same order they have to be put into the foundation (first "
"the aces, then the twos, &etc;) Typically, you want to avoid emptying a "
"column until the last card is ready to be moved to a foundation."
msgstr ""
"Če želite rešiti to igro, je priporočljivo, da zgrabite karte iz igralnih "
"zaporedij v istem vrstnem redu, kot jih morate dati v temelj (najprej asi, "
"nato dvojke itd.). Običajno se želite izogniti praznjenju stolpca, dokler "
"zadnja karta je pripravljena za premik na temelj."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:616
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Castle</title>"
msgstr "<title>Grad</title>"

#. Tag: primary
#: index.docbook:618
#, no-c-format
msgid "<primary>Castle</primary>"
msgstr "<primary>Grad</primary>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:618
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Castle is a family of patience or solitaire card games typically played with "
"a deck of 52 playing cards. It is sometimes described as \"Freecell without "
"cells\" because its game play is similar but without extra empty spaces to "
"maneuver in most variations."
msgstr ""
"Castle je družina iger potrpežljivosti ali pasjans, ki se običajno igrajo s "
"kompletom 52 igralnih kart. Včasih jo opisujejo kot \"prosto celico brez "
"celic\", ker je njena igra podobna, vendar brez dodatnih praznih prostorov "
"za manevriranje v večini različic."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:622
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The object of the game is to build all the cards onto the four foundations "
"by suit, each from ace to king."
msgstr ""
"Cilj igre je sestaviti vse karte na štiri temelje po barvi, vsako od asa do "
"kralja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:633
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<quote>Beleaguered Castle</quote>. Aces are dealt to the foundations. Any "
"card can fill empty spaces."
msgstr ""
"<quote>Oblegani grad</quote>. Asi se delijo do temeljev. Vsaka karta lahko "
"zapolni prazne prostore."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:634
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<quote>Citadel</quote> is like <quote>Beleaguered Castle</quote>, but "
"matching cards are moved to the foundation during the deal, leaving uneven "
"piles."
msgstr ""
"<quote>Citadela</quote> je kot <quote>Oblegani grad</quote>, vendar se "
"ujemajoče se karte med delitvijo premaknejo na temelj, tako da ostanejo "
"neenakomerni kupčki."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:635
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<quote>Exiled Kings</quote> is like <quote>Citadel</quote>, but only kings "
"can fill empty spaces."
msgstr ""
"<quote>Izgnani kralji</quote> je kot <quote>Citadela</quote>, vendar samo "
"kralji lahko zapolnijo prazne prostore."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:636
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<quote>Siegecraft</quote> is like <quote>Beleaguered Castle</quote>, but "
"with one free cell."
msgstr ""
"<quote>Obrt obleganja</quote> je kot <quote>Oblegani grad</quote>, vendar z "
"eno prosto celico."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:637
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<quote>Streets and Alleys</quote> is like <quote>Beleaguered Castle</quote>, "
"but aces are included in shuffling."
msgstr ""
"<quote>Ulice in aleje</quote> je kot <quote>Oblegani grad</quote>, vendar so "
"asi vključeni v mešanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:638
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<quote>Stronghold</quote> is like <quote>Streets and Alleys</quote>, but "
"with one free cell."
msgstr ""
"<quote>Utrdba</quote> je kot <quote>Ulice in ulice</quote>, vendar z eno "
"prosto celico."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:641
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To solve this game it is recommended to build evenly on the foundations. Try "
"to create empty piles which can be used to facilitate longer moves to free "
"up buried cards."
msgstr ""
"Za rešitev te igre je priporočljivo graditi enakomerno na temeljih. "
"Poskusite ustvariti prazne kupčke, ki jih lahko uporabite za omogočanje "
"daljših premikov, da sprostite zakopane karte."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:651
#, no-c-format
msgid "Interface Overview"
msgstr "Pregled vmesnika"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:654
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Game Menu"
msgstr "Meni igre"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:657
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>N</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Game…</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>N</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nova igra…</"
"guimenuitem >"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:662
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Return to the game selection screen.</action> This action abandons "
"the deal in progress."
msgstr ""
"<action>Vrnitev na zaslon za izbiro igre.</action> To dejanje opusti igro v "
"teku."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:665
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Deal</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Novo deljenje</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:670
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Start a new deal of the same game type.</action> This action "
"abandons the deal in progress."
msgstr ""
"<action>Začni novo deljenje iste vrste igre.</action> To dejanje opusti "
"deljenje v teku."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:673
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Numbered Deal…</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Novo oštevilčeno deljenje…</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:679
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Start a new deal by specifying the game type and deal number.</"
"action> This action abandons the deal in progress."
msgstr ""
"<action>Začnite novo deljenje tako, da navedete vrsto igre in številko "
"deljenja.</action> To dejanje opusti deljenje v teku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:680
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kpatience; gives each deal a unique indentifying number (which it uses "
"internally to randomize the deck during the initial deal). This feature "
"allows you to replay a deal of interest or to attempt a particularly "
"difficult deal recommended by a friend. Especially dedicated players may "
"wish to <quote>beat</quote> &kpatience; by playing all 2147483647 deals "
"consecutively for each of the game types."
msgstr ""
"&kpatience; vsakemu razdelku dodeli edinstveno identifikacijsko številko (ki "
"jo interno uporablja za naključno razvrščanje kompleta med začetnim "
"razdelitvijo). Ta funkcija vam omogoča, da ponovno predvajate deljenje, ki "
"vas zanima, ali poskusite s posebno težkim deljenjem, ki ga priporoča "
"prijatelj. Še posebej predani igralci bodo morda želeli <quote>premagati</"
"quote> &kpatience; z igranjem vseh 2147483647 deljenj zaporedoma za vsako "
"vrsto igre."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:681
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that for Freecell, &kpatience;'s deal numbers match those described in "
"<ulink url=\"http://www.solitairelaboratory.com/fcfaq.html\">the Freecell "
"&FAQ;</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da se za Freecell številke &kpatience; ujemajo s tistimi, ki so "
"opisane v <ulink url=\"http://www.solitairelaboratory.com/fcfaq.html"
"\">Freecell &FAQ;</ulink>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:685
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F5</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Restart Deal</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F5</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Ponovno deljenje</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:690
#, no-c-format
msgid "Return the current game to its initially dealt condition."
msgstr "Vrni trenutno igro na prvotno razdeljeno stanje."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:693
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Load…</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Naloži…</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:698
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Load a saved game.</action> This action abandons the deal in "
"progress."
msgstr ""
"<action>Naloži shranjeno igro.</action> To dejanje opusti deljenje v teku."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:701
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Load Recent</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem><replaceable>List of recently accessed files</replaceable></"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Naloži nedavne</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem><replaceable>Seznam nedavno dostopanih datotek</replaceable></"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:706
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>List recently accessed save files in order of last use.</action> "
"Selecting a game will load it. This action abandons the deal in progress."
msgstr ""
"<action>Seznam nedavno dostopanih shranjenih datotek po vrstnem redu zadnje "
"uporabe.</action> Če izberete igro, se bo naložila. To dejanje opusti "
"deljenje v teku."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:709
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save As…</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shrani kot…</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:714
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save the current game to disk."
msgstr "Shranite trenutno igro na disk."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:717
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Statistics</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Statistika</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:721
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Display various statistics about your performance broken down by game type."
msgstr ""
"Prikažite različne statistične podatke o vaši uspešnosti, razčlenjene po "
"vrsti igre."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:724
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zapusti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:729
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Quit</action> &kpatience;."
msgstr "<action>Zapusti</action> &kpatience;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:734
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Move Menu"
msgstr "Meni Premakni"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:737
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Move</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Undo</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Premakni</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Razveljavi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:742
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Undo</action> your last move."
msgstr "<action>Razveljavi</action> svojo zadnjo potezo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:745
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>Z</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Move</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Redo</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>Z</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Premakni</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ponovi</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:750
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Redo</action> the move that was just undone by <guimenuitem>Undo</"
"guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"<action>Ponovi</action> potezo, ki je bila pravkar razveljavljena z "
"<guimenuitem>Razveljavi</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:753
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>H</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Move</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Hint</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>H</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Premakni</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Namig</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:758
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Provide some hints as to possible moves, should the player become stuck. "
"Cards that can be legally moved to another pile are temporarily highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Podajte nekaj namigov o možnih potezah, če se igralec zatakne. Karte, ki jih "
"je mogoče zakonito premakniti na drug kup, so začasno označene."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:761
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>D</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Move</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Demo</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>D</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Premakni</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Demo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:766
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Start the demo mode.</action> While in demo mode, &kpatience; "
"attempts to solve the deal for you. Activate this action a second time to "
"exit demo mode."
msgstr ""
"<action>Zaženite demo način.</action> Ko ste v demo načinu, &kpatience; "
"poskuša rešiti posel namesto vas. Drugič aktivirajte to dejanje, da "
"zapustite predstavitveni način."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:769
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut>&Space;</shortcut> <guimenu>Move</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Draw</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut>&Space;</shortcut> <guimenu>Premakni</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Potegni</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:774
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Flip one of more cards from the talon and move them to the waste "
"pile.</action> This action is available in only certain games."
msgstr ""
"<action>Obrnite eno ali več kart iz talona in jih premaknite na kup smeti.</"
"action> To dejanje je na voljo samo v nekaterih igrah."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:777
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut>&Enter;</shortcut> <guimenu>Move</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Deal Row</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut>&Enter;</shortcut> <guimenu>Premakni</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Vrstica deljenja</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:782
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Flip several cards from the talon and place one on each playing pile."
"</action> This action is available in only certain games."
msgstr ""
"<action>Obrnite več kart iz talona in položite eno na vsak igralni kup.</"
"action> To dejanje je na voljo samo v določenih igrah."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:785
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>R</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Move</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Redeal</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>R</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Premakni</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Ponovno deljenje</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:790
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Collect all the card left in play and redeal them without shuffling."
"</action> This action is available in only certain games."
msgstr ""
"<action>Zberite vse karte, ki so ostale v igri, in jih znova razdelite brez "
"mešanja.</action> To dejanje je na voljo samo v določenih igrah."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:795
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Settings and Help Menu"
msgstr "Meni Nastavitve in pomoč"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:796
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Apart from the common &kde; Settings and Help menus described in the <ulink "
"url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html\">Menu</ulink> chapter of the &kde; "
"Fundamentals documentation &kpatience; has these application specific menu "
"entries:"
msgstr ""
"Poleg običajnega &kde; Meniji Nastavitve in Pomoč, opisani v poglavju <ulink "
"url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html\">Meni</ulink> v &kde; Dokumentacija o "
"osnovah &kpatience; ima te menijske vnose za posamezne aplikacije:"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:801
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guisubmenu><replaceable>Game Type Options</"
"replaceable></guisubmenu> <guimenuitem><replaceable>List of game type "
"specific options</replaceable></guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guisubmenu><replaceable>Možnosti vrste igre</"
"replaceable></guisubmenu> <guimenuitem><replaceable>Seznam posebnih možnosti "
"vrste igre</replaceable></guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:806
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>List options specific to the current game type.</action> This menu "
"is available in only certain games (Klondike and Spider)."
msgstr ""
"<action>Seznam možnosti, značilnih za trenutno vrsto igre.</action> Ta meni "
"je na voljo samo v nekaterih igrah (Klondike in Pajek)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:809
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Stack Options</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Face Down (harder)/Face Up (easier)</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Možnosti sklada</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Obrnjeno navzdol (težje)/obrnjeno navzgor (lažje)</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:814
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Allows you to choose if the card faces should be shown.</action> "
"This menu is available in Spider only."
msgstr ""
"<action>Omogoča vam, da izberete, ali naj bodo obrazi kartic prikazani.</"
"action> Ta meni je na voljo samo v Pajku."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:817
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Enable Autodrop</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Omogoči samodejni polaganje</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:821
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enable automatically moving cards to the foundation piles when possible."
msgstr ""
"Omogočite samodejno premikanje kartic na temeljne skupke, ko je to mogoče."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:824
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Enable Solver</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Omogoči reševalca</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:828
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Enable the automatic solving engine.</action> When enabled, the "
"solver will constantly try to determine whether the current game state is "
"winnable. You may wish to disable the solver to conserve processor or "
"battery usage."
msgstr ""
"<action>Omogoči mehanizem za samodejno reševanje.</action> Ko je omogočen, "
"bo reševalec nenehno poskušal ugotoviti, ali je trenutno stanje igre mogoče "
"zmagati. Morda boste želeli onemogočiti reševalca, da prihranite procesor "
"ali porabo baterije."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:831
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Play Sounds</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Predvajaj zvoke</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:835
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Sounds are played when you taken or place cards.</action> More "
"sounds are expected in the future."
msgstr ""
"<action>Zvoki se predvajajo, ko vzamete ali položite karte.</action> V "
"prihodnosti pričakujemo več zvokov."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:838
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Remember State on Exit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zapomni si stanje ob izhodu</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:842
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Enable automatic saving of the game state when &kpatience; is shut "
"down.</action> If enabled, &kpatience; will load the previous game state "
"automatically the next time it is started."
msgstr ""
"<action>Omogoči samodejno shranjevanje stanja igre, ko &kpatience; je "
"izklopljen.</action> Če je omogočeno, &kpatience; ob naslednjem zagonu "
"samodejno naloži prejšnje stanje igre."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:845
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>F1</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Help</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Help with Current "
"Game</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>F1</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pomoč pri "
"trenutni igri</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:850
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens the section with the Rules for the current game in this handbook."
msgstr "Odpre razdelek s pravili za trenutno igro v tem priročniku."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:857
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently asked questions"
msgstr "Pogosto zastavljena vprašanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:862
#, no-c-format
msgid "I want to change the way this game looks. Can I?"
msgstr "Želim spremeniti videz te igre. Ali lahko?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:863
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can change the faces and backs of the playing cards and the game theme. "
"To do so please use <menuchoice> <shortcut><keycap>F10</keycap></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Change Appearance…</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> on the menubar."
msgstr ""
"Spremenite lahko obraze in hrbtne strani igralnih kart ter temo igre. Za to "
"uporabite <menuchoice> <shortcut><keycap>F10</keycap></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Spremeni videz…</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> v menijski vrstici ."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:870
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I use the keyboard to play the game?"
msgstr "Ali lahko uporabljam tipkovnico za igranje igre?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:871
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"No, &kpatience; features no keyboard only play. However, most menu options "
"do have keyboard shortcuts."
msgstr ""
"Ne, &kpatience; ne vsebuje samo igranja s tipkovnico. Vendar ima večina "
"možnosti menija bližnjice na tipkovnici."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:874
#, no-c-format
msgid "Even with hints I still have no clue how to play. Help!"
msgstr "Tudi z namigi še vedno nimam pojma, kako igrati. pomoč!"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:875
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Besides the <quote>Hint</quote> feature there also is a useful <quote>Demo</"
"quote> mode, where the built-in artificial intelligence will play the game "
"for you. You can try to watch and learn. However, if you have any questions "
"it is better to read the <link linkend=\"howto\">How to Play</link> and "
"<link linkend=\"rules_and_tips\">Game Rules, Strategies and Tips</link> "
"sections of this handbook."
msgstr ""
"Poleg funkcije <quote>Namig</quote> obstaja tudi uporaben način <quote>Demo</"
"quote>, kjer bo vgrajena umetna inteligenca igrala igro namesto vas. Lahko "
"poskusite gledati in se učiti. Če pa imate kakršna koli vprašanja, je bolje, "
"da preberete razdelka <link linkend=\"howto\">Kako igrati</link> in <link "
"linkend=\"rules_and_tips\">Pravila, strategije in nasveti</link> tega "
"priročnika."

